Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.16,0:00:03.13,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A racing second hand, a shooting comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.13,0:00:06.93,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Conan's logic will moisten hearts\Ndried by modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.93,0:00:10.57,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's proof is quite unique!\NLet's change our way of thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.57,0:00:12.31,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.31,0:00:14.31,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.31,0:00:16.89,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:49.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm done with my bath, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you busy tomorrow, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:54.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I have no plans. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:57.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of Dad's friends just called
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.48,0:02:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and invited us over for a barbecue tomorrow afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.38,0:02:05.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name's Teraoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He really watched over me when I was a police detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:16.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now he's chief inspector of Investigation Section #4.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.93,0:02:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the group in charge of handling gangs! I'll come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.77,0:02:25.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Real police detectives have lots of interesting stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:27.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.05,0:02:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd always say my logic was wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:41.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but then you'd wind up being wrong yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:44.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's still like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now you're a famous detective! To be honest, it's hard to believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:54.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please give me some credit...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:56.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, have some—Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:03:01.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You haven't had a drop to drink!\NThat's not like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:06.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm off duty, but there's no telling what might come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.65,0:03:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is an awesome car! It must be expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:21.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cars are my only hobby,\Nso I spend my money on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:25.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}. Did you have something to do today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:26.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for calling out of the blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He suddenly decided last night and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:37.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 9:00, he left his room and said, "I'm bringing Mouri over tomorrow!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He normally plans things out well in advance...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just thought it would be nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:03.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:13.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright! I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.91,0:04:17.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't tell anyone! I'll come alone! Alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:26.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was Matsuyama, a gang leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:34.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently, he accidentally killed someone last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's wanted to change his ways, and I've been giving him advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:43.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to convince him to turn himself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All by yourself? That's not a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he were to run away, you'd be held responsible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's dangerous! You should contact HQ and—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:05:00.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't! I promised I would go alone and tell no one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:03.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you're off duty, and without a gun—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:08.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't need a gun! He called me out of trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:11.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't betray that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:13.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'm coming with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:17.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I'll call Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, fine. But only I'll meet him! Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:28.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. So where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:31.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kowan Wharf, Warehouse 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get my jacket. Wait by the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get your jacket!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:40.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! You just stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:53.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's taking him so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:03.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry. It took a while to find the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:11.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:28.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What was that sound? Could it have been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will Dad be all right after having all that alcohol?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:35.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}! Let's go to Kowan Wharf too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:39.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're worried about him, aren't you?! I'll get a taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.53,0:06:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:43.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:46.86,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kowan Wharf
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:57.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.07,0:07:00.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry! We were worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:01.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Teraoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He told me to wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:09.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's check it out, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:13.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?! That would put him in—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:18.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:20.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meaning the other guy does!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Senpai{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.82,0:07:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So when you tried to get him to turn himself in,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he pulled out a gun and demanded your money and credit cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:55.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. It seems he planned to skip the country...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.11,0:08:02.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told him he'd never get away, and that we should talk it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:06.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I put my hands up and walked slowly toward him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:12.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I jumped at him and tried to snatch the gun away—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:14.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,—when it went off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:23.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just an unfortunate accident,\NInspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:26.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who exactly did Matsuyama kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:30.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know his name,\Nbut he said he was a gambling client.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:33.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And your relation with Matsuyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:38.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They had talked about him getting out of a life of crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.61,0:08:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he came alone to meet him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:46.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was another mistake. I take full responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My judgment was too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Senpai{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:56.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If my theory is correct, this was no accident. It was a murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:59.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Teraoka{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} is the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:04.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But there's no proof of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:08.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:10.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:16.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've probably already seen on TV or in the papers,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:20.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but Matsuyama's victim was indeed a gambling client.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder happened around 8:00, two nights ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:26.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the weapon was a knife, not a gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. We still don't know why he didn't use a gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it looks like a gambling debt\Nwas at the root of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:41.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about Teraoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r}'s involvement?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:47.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A formal decision is forthcoming,\Nbut he did go alone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:51.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and allowed Matsuyama to die, accident or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll probably lose a few months' pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:56.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:10:01.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Which means nobody doubts Teraoka{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s testimony...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, there is one thing we've kept from the media—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:09.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we found three sets of fingerprints on the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three sets?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One is Matsuyama's, and another is Inspector Teraoka's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've determined that his prints got there during the struggle,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:24.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but we don't know who the others belong to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:27.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe from someone in Matsuyama's gang?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:32.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. We got all their prints, but none matched up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe an unrelated arms dealer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:41.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've considered that too, but we don't have any leads.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:49.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who does the third set belong to?\NIf that gun's owner is who I suspect it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:55.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector! You told Teraoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} about those fingerprints, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:57.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did he look at the time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:11:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it,\Nhe seemed extremely shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:09.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No doubt about it!\NMatsuyama was shot by Teraoka{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:11.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The third set of prints is the proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teraoka residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:25.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:28.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to discuss yesterday's incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:35.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was weird for Inspector Megure to ask me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:38.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to come to Teraoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r}'s house at this hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And me and Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!\NI wonder if something happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:47.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And I called the inspector using the old man's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:49.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Everything's all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:56.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know the inspector had called you here too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I don't know why he called us here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:05.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:07.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a show I wanna see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a TV you can watch in the spare room upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:15.00,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yaiba Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:19.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This room is for when we have guests over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:22.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You and Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} should come spend the night sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:23.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:44.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So this is Teraoka{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:02.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's only one missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:05.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's in the trash?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A felt rag?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.42,0:13:17.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Smells of oil. Did he use the inside of this to—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what did you have to say, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:30.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who had something to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:36.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! You called me and said you had something to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the one who called me was—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:42.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here we go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well. Let us forget the details and get down to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But first, please have a seat, madam. You too, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:14:02.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teraoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r}. You killed Matsuyama, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:10.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never expected you to say that!\NI see you haven't changed one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:16.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you met Matsuyama,\Nyou hit him with a knockout blow,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:22.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,put the gun in his hand, aimed it at his chest, and pulled the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:25.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:29.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous! What kind of joke is this, Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, when you invited us to the barbecue yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you didn't take even a single sip of beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already told you—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:45.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Just as you said, even off-duty officers don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:47.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when they might be called in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you refrained from drinking. I thought so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:58.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, you were very intent on checking the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:04.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps because you knew when Matsuyama would call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you left your phone on your belt and didn't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I always have my phone on me! In case I get an emergency call!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:17.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:20.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's in my room now, but normally it's—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:24.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, when you spoke with Matsuyama on the phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:29.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you whispered at first but then started to shout!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:30.99,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:38.23,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Where are you?! Alright! I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:43.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Almost as if to let us hear what was being discussed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:50.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, even though you were in a hurry,\Nwhen I asked you about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:55.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you purposely stopped and explained the call in great detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.82,0:15:59.59,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That was Matsuyama, a gang leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:03.46,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Apparently, he accidentally killed someone last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:08.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But half of what you said was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he really called you\Nabout his murder the night before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:20.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then made arrangements with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:26.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One was to call you at 12:00 the following day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:30.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the person he talked to was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually him, during the whispering.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He acted the rest out by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:39.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The caller had probably hung up by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:43.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, anticipating I would suggest going together,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he said he would meet Matsuyama alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that I would vouch that you met him unarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:17:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you needed me near you when he called.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:07.82,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He suddenly decided last night and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:12.16,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}At 9:00, he left his room and said, "I'm bringing Mouri over tomorrow!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:18.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, I was used as part of your plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! He didn't have the gun
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when he got out of the car at Kowan Wharf, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:30.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seemed that way to me, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:35.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He purposely didn't wear his jacket to make it seem that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:41.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,despite having gone through the trouble of getting it before leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:44.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So where was the gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Attached to his right ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had hidden the gun in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:18:00.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he ardently refused\Nwhen his wife offered to get his jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:03.71,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No! You just stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:06.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well? Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is all speculation; you have no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:12.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It won't hold up in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:19.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there is proof. The third set of fingerprints on the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:21.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The third set of fingerprints?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As we waited for you to come back out yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,your wife looked uneasily up at the upstairs room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:35.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time, I thought she was just worried
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:41.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because you were going to meet Matsuyama without a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:51.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was worried because you were going to meet him with a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.93,0:18:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, she knew you had a gun hidden in your room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:05.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, she found your gun by accident
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:08.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and picked it up without thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:11.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then she quickly put it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:16.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She probably wanted to ask about it but was too afraid to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and continued to live in constant uneasiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:28.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Clueless about this, you took the gun and killed Matsuyama
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in a fake accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:38.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The third set of fingerprints belonged to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:41.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:43.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is exactly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:45.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Misako!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:57.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you care to explain your motive for killing Matsuyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me he was—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,—paying me off. I leaked police info to him in exchange for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:06.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just pocket change and unimportant info at first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:15.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I grew more and more numb to it all, and before I realized it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had gone beyond the point of no return.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:23.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I got a call from him\Nat around 8:00 two nights ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:29.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had killed someone. He wanted money to skip the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:33.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said if he got caught, I would go down too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I decided to kill him then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told him I'd have the money\Nthe next day and to call me at 12:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:51.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had secretly kept the gun should any such situation come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rest was all as Mouri said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize for my treachery.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.35,0:22:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,People sure do change. Like Teraoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.85,0:22:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you heard what he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.02,0:22:48.66,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You really have become a great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.66,0:22:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looked kind of happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.00,0:22:53.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:22:56.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess he's really—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.90,0:23:02.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know how Teraoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} hid the gun in a video case?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.84,0:23:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have any dangerous stuff hidden, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.85,0:23:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.45,0:23:16.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.36,0:23:19.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something else inside it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.46,0:23:26.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.24,0:23:30.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.44,0:23:34.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blame them, not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.57,0:23:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.34,0:23:38.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.85,0:23:42.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't hide those there!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.32,0:23:49.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Was this man's kid abducted?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.56,0:23:52.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad! You have a clue about the kidnapper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.53,0:23:57.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is by lots of crabs and a bubble-spouting whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.83,0:24:00.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This license plate is fake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.90,0:24:04.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no! Once the kidnapper gets the money, Keita{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10} is—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.24,0:24:08.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it! The crabs and the whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.90,0:24:14.91,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.91,0:24:19.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Chairs and Tables
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.07,0:24:21.71,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The next episode title's a bit odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.71,0:24:23.71,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Can you "crab" me the time? It's "whale" late!{this is a stupid joke. "time" (jikan) mutated into "crab" (kani), "9:00" (ku-ji) into "whale" (kujira). anyone doing an XTL may want to keep this in mind.}
